### Scorely API requests (VS Code / JetBrains HTTP client)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/v1

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create Song
POST {{baseUrl}}/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "HTTP Client Song",
  "artist": "HTTP Client Artist",
  "album_art": null,
  "genre": null,
  "release_year": 2026
}

### List Songs
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Song Detail (set your id)
@songId = aaaaaaaa-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/{{songId}}

### Create Rating (requires auth in production; works with DEV_BYPASS_AUTH)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "song_id": "{{songId}}",
  "rating_value": 5,
  "review": "Great track"
}

### My Ratings
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/ratings

### Bookmark Song
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "song_id": "{{songId}}"
}

### My Bookmarks
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks

### Update My Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "http_client_user"
}

### Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/profile

### Log Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "synthwave 2021"
}

### My Search History
GET {{baseUrl}}/searches

### Activity Feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/activity/feed
